---
import Docs from '../../layouts/Docs.astro';
---
<Docs title="API Setup" active="/docs/api-setup">
  <h1 style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;">API Setup</h1>
  <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:32px;">
    Configure API keys for AI-powered features.
  </p>

  <div style="padding:14px;background:rgba(0,212,170,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(0,212,170,0.2);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:32px;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--green);line-height:1.7;margin:0;">
      <strong>Good news:</strong> Charts, prices, portfolio tracker, and risk calculator all work without any API keys. Market data feeds are included out of the box.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- AI Engine -->
  <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
    <span style="color:var(--amber);">AI Engine API Key</span> — Signal Generation
  </h2>
  <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;">
    Required for the AI Trade Signal generator. Set the <code style="background:var(--bg3);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;font-size:12px;color:var(--amber);">GROQ_API_KEY</code> in your server <code style="background:var(--bg3);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;font-size:12px;">.env</code> file.
  </p>

  <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:10px;">Setup:</h3>
  <ol style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text2);line-height:2.2;padding-left:20px;margin-bottom:16px;">
    <li>Obtain an API key from your AI provider</li>
    <li>Add it to your <code style="background:var(--bg3);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;font-size:12px;">.env</code> file as <code style="background:var(--bg3);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;font-size:12px;color:var(--amber);">GROQ_API_KEY=your_key_here</code></li>
    <li>Restart the server</li>
  </ol>

  <div style="background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:32px;">
    <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Rate Limits</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;">
      <div style="padding:8px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:6px;">
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);">Rate Limit</div>
        <div style="font-size:14px;font-family:var(--font-mono);color:var(--green);">30 req/min</div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:8px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:6px;">
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);">Daily Limit</div>
        <div style="font-size:14px;font-family:var(--font-mono);color:var(--green);">14,400 req/day</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Summary -->
  <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);">Data Sources Summary</h2>
  <div style="overflow-x:auto;">
    <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;">
      <thead>
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
          <th style="text-align:left;padding:10px 12px;color:var(--text3);font-weight:500;font-size:11px;">Service</th>
          <th style="text-align:left;padding:10px 12px;color:var(--text3);font-weight:500;font-size:11px;">Purpose</th>
          <th style="text-align:left;padding:10px 12px;color:var(--text3);font-weight:500;font-size:11px;">Cost</th>
          <th style="text-align:left;padding:10px 12px;color:var(--text3);font-weight:500;font-size:11px;">Key Required</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {[
          { api: 'Crypto Feed',    purpose: 'Crypto prices & OHLC', cost: 'Included', key: 'No', color: 'var(--green)' },
          { api: 'Forex Feed',     purpose: 'Currency exchange rates', cost: 'Included', key: 'No', color: 'var(--blue)' },
          { api: 'Stocks Feed',    purpose: 'Stock prices & OHLC', cost: 'Included', key: 'No', color: 'var(--purple)' },
          { api: 'AI Engine',      purpose: 'Trade signal generation', cost: 'Included', key: 'Yes', color: 'var(--amber)' },
        ].map(row => (
          <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
            <td style={`padding:10px 12px;font-weight:500;color:${row.color};`}>{row.api}</td>
            <td style="padding:10px 12px;color:var(--text2);">{row.purpose}</td>
            <td style="padding:10px 12px;color:var(--text2);font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;">{row.cost}</td>
            <td style="padding:10px 12px;color:var(--text2);">{row.key}</td>
          </tr>
        ))}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</Docs>
